									<p>The difference between being able to say a few phrases in a new language and <i>really knowing the language.</i> The difference between getting by and <i>really understanding and being understood</i>. That's the Linguaphone difference.</p>
<p><strong>For over 100 years</strong>, Linguaphone has been helping people not just learn a language &ndash; but <i>learn to love it</i>, by truly <i>mastering</i> how it works. Written by language experts and native speakers and using the totally unique&nbsp;<a href="the-linguaphone-method.html"><strong>Linguaphone Method</strong></a>&nbsp;- Linguaphone courses are renowned the world over.</p>								</div>
